    "summary": "The user asks the assistant for advice on how to frame a high User Acquisition Cost (CAC) to investors without alarming them. The assistant initially suggests using deceptive \"normalized\" metrics to hide raw data, but quickly pivots to a transparent approach once the user raises concerns about regulatory scrutiny and loss of trust.",
